Name: OtherValue
Description: When the value of Delimiter is "other" provide the character used for delimiting values here. Spaces and binary values are not allowed.

Name: TreatConsecutiveDelimiterAsOne
Description: Defines the default value for the delimiter used to separate variables in a delimited record. The attribute treatConsecutiveDelimiterAsOne indicates how consecutive delimiters should be handed by the software.

Name: DelimiterTypeValue
Enumeration: space tab comma semicolon colon pipe other
